; Regression test for issue #723: -S t doesn't sort timelog entries correctly
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/723
;
; When sorting balance output by total (-S t), accounts with hierarchical
; names (containing colons) were not sorted correctly.  The sort expression
; 't' evaluates 'amount', which for parent accounts with no direct postings
; returned zero instead of the family total, causing them to sort first
; regardless of their children's totals.

